Key Match Events: Youssef En-Nesyri scored two goals (30th and 55th minutes)
Sofiane Boufal scored a goal (35th minute)
Miscellaneous Highlights: This match is part of the national team’s preparations for the 2023 AFCON, scheduled from January 13 to February 11 in Côte d'Ivoire
